// GameData:/Fx/Bank/Basics/AoA_BANK_Bomb_ShockWave.ndf
// Call Test_Bomb_ShockWave in FX Tester
// ShockWave Effect on ground

export Test_Bomb_ShockWave is Competition
(
    Actions =
    [
        Template_ActionCall
        (
            Action = ~/BANK_Bomb_ShockWave
            LocalVariables = []
            NamedParameters = MAP[
                ( 'parFinalSize', 10000 ),
                ( 'parDuration', 1 ),
            ]
        ),
    ]
)

export BANK_Bomb_ShockWave is SimultaneousActionDeclaration
(
    Params =
    [
        parInitialSize          is Template_Param_Float ( DefaultValue = 200 ),
        parFinalSize            is Template_Param_Float ( DefaultValue = 1500 ),
        parDuration             is Template_Param_Float ( DefaultValue = 0.5 ),
        parPosition             is Template_Param_Float3( DefaultValue = float3[0,0,0] ),
        parZBias                is Template_Param_Float ( DefaultValue = 255 ),
        parUpVector             is Template_Param_Float3( DefaultValue = float3[0,0,1] ),
        parCount                is Template_Param_Int( DefaultValue = 1 ),
    ]
    Actions =
    [
        private ShockWave is ParticleBombSpawner
        (
            ParticleMaxDurationForSpawnSkip = parDuration * 1.1
            Count = parCount
            Spawner =  ParticleSpawner
            (
                Initialisers =
                [
                    ParticleInitialiserList
                    (
                        Size = 300
                        ColorModifier = float3[1, 1, 1]
                        Alpha = 1.0

                        UpVector = parUpVector
                        Opacity = 0
                        Position = parPosition
                        ColorRGB = LinearColor[1, 1, 1]
                        Rotation = RandomUnit
                        CustomFloat_1 = parInitialSize * HomogeneousUnit
                        CustomFloat_2 = parFinalSize * HomogeneousUnit
                        CustomFloat_3 = parZBias
                    )
                ]
                ParticleLifetime = parDuration
                ParticleDescriptor = ParticleDescriptor
                (
                    RenderInfo = ParticleRenderInfo
                    (
                        ZTest = True
                        ZWrite = False
                        SortTriangles = True
                        Use3DRotation = False
                        TextureName = 'GameData:/Assets/2D/Fx/ring.png'
                        EmissiveParticle = true
                    )
                    Evolvers = ParticleStandardEvolverList
                    (
                        ColorMultiplier = MapToLinearSmoothRect[ParticleLifeRatio, 0, 0.2, 0.5, 1] * 0.025
                        Alpha = MapToLinearSmoothRect[ParticleLifeRatio, 0, 0.2, 0.5, 1]
                        Size = lerp[ParticleLifeRatio, ParticleCustomFloat_1, ParticleCustomFloat_2]
                        ZBias = ParticleCustomFloat_3
                    )
                    ParticleRenderer = Template_ParticleRendererPlane(StickOnGround = true)
                )
            )
        ),
    ]
)
